“commencement of this Act” means, in relation to an establishment or
                                employment, the date on which this Act comes into force in respect
                                of that establishment or employment;

require any employer to produce any register, mister-roll or
                                    other documents relating to the employment of workers, and
                                    examine such documents;

registers and other documents which an employer is required under
                                    Section 8 to maintain in relation to the workers employed by
                                    him;
